cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.SE 

This paper proposes a security framework for the ADS-B communication technology used in aviation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also deals with wireless communication and network protocols, which suggests the categories cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The proposed framework leverages the \muTESLA protocol, which is a cryptographic protocol, and the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests the categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
